<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>8</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a yuàn nǐ lā zhe wǒ men de shǒu, zài fēng yǔ zhōng xíng chí;
 zhǔ a yuàn nǐ qiān zhe wǒ men de xīn, fēi wǎng shì jiè gè de.
 yuàn nǐ de jīng bīng cóng zhè lǐ zǒu chū, yuàn nǐ de duì wǔ zài zhè lǐ jué qǐ,
 yuàn jiāng fú yīn de huǒ bǎ chuán biàn tiān yá, chuán biàn de de sì jí
 zǒu zǒu zǒu, gēn suí nǐ! pǎo pǎo pǎo, gēn suí nǐ!
 yǒu yī tiān zhōng huá yào xìng qǐ, yǒu yī tiān zhōng huá yào xìng qǐ!
 chōng pò nà jǐn bì de dà mén, gōng pò nà jiān gù de yíng lěi;
 fú yīn de qí zhì jiāng zài zhōng huá piāo yáng, jiào huì yào hé yī! hé yī!</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a yuàn nǐ lā zhe wǒ men de shǒu 迦南8</title>
</song>